    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "riomam",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-riomom004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。お母さんの夢はその次でいいからね\n今度こそ、いい人を連れて来てちょうだい？",
      "startTime": 208.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 212.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　お母さん、それってどういう……",
      "startTime": 212.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "riomam",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-riomom005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、私が気付かないとでも思ったの？\n会った瞬間から、分かってたわよ",
      "startTime": 220.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 223.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
