      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかしてお母さん、気付いてたの？\nこの人が、本当は私の彼氏じゃないって……",
      "startTime": 226.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "riomam",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-riomom006.m4a",
      "text": "何年、あなたの母親をやってると思ってるの？\nそんなの当たり前でしょ",
      "startTime": 233.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
