      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 238.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "riomam",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-riomom007.m4a",
      "text": "可愛い娘の反応を楽しみたくて、ふざけちゃったけど\nやり過ぎちゃったわ。ごめんなさいね",
      "startTime": 242.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですか……\nさすが莉央さんのお母さんですね。俺達より上手だ……",
      "startTime": 247.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 252.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……忘れてたわ\nお母さんに隠し事なんて出来ないってこと……",
      "startTime": 255.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 259.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "riomam",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-riomom008.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、次回を楽しみにしているわ\nもちろん、{user}さんでもいいのよ？",
      "startTime": 262.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 266.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "もう！　お母さん、何言ってるのよ！\n恥ずかしいでしょ！　貴方も何を笑っているのよ！？",
      "startTime": 269.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 273.2333333333
    },
    {
