      "speakerCode": "riomam",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-riomom009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、二人とも元気でね\n莉央、またあなたの歌を聴きに行くわ",
      "startTime": 276.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio026.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～……全く、うちの母親ときたら……",
      "startTime": 280.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 285.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio027.m4a",
      "text": "分かったわよ！　いつでも好きなだけ\n聴きに来てちょうだい！　いつでも待ってるから！",
